OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome bright
OL,6,Fspells possible in the west at first.
OL,7,FOtherwise dull and cloudy through the
OL,8,Fevening and overnight with perhaps
OL,9,Fsome patchy light drizzle in places.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FA dry and rather cloudy day,
OL,12,Fbut some bright or sunny spells will
OL,13,Fbreak through during the afternoon.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,16,Fto Wednesday will be dry with sunny
OL,17,Fspells and becoming warmer inland,
OL,18,Fcooler and cloudier at times along
OL,19,Fimmediate coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
